name: HEN NOT DEAD
description:
This digital painting responds to yesterday's hicetnunc which was busy because it was instantly inaccessible to users, both collectors and artists themselves. In my opinion, when hicetnunc cannot be accessed, it does not mean that we also stop working. Working for me is a complex thing, aka cannot depend on the market. if you make a work for a nominal, it means you depend on money and make it the key of all keys
3508 X 4960 PX
PIQREE
